window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They say that behind every great man is a great woman, but what if that woman is a werewolf? </p> <p>Terry and Char cross the Wastelands returning to New Boulder carrying a message of hope. They'd found a better place. Could they move the whole town there, and would it be safer? </p> <p>They have a lead on Terry's white whale, a secure military facility. </p> <p>What will they find and can they break in? </p> <p>The Forsaken, the vampires of the new world, aren't afraid of a werewolf or her mate. But Terry and Char aren't afraid of the Forsaken either. </p>"; 
